{"tid":2090271,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"四川水災咁嚴重，唔知道四川辣王 屎萊姆捐咗錢未？","createTime":"2020-07-02T05:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T13:07:07.000Z","uid":187192,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9294315ad2e754852aecb88a570833c199f20b25","tid":2090271,"uid":187192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"依家四川水災情況咁嚴重, 四川辣王屎萊姆生於斯長於斯,唔係唔捐錢咁衰仔下話?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人哋Ming 仔, 大拿拿捐左20萬零1蚊。<br />\n我唔信四川辣王會食中國四川人既人血饅頭, 但係萬一我偶像真係冇捐錢,食中國人人血饅頭嘅話,我一定會擺佢上微博,同公安舉報佢犯咗國安法。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以幫手問下辣王捐咗幾多錢？<br />\n相信屎屎一定係一名愛國愛港嘅youtuber, 希望屎屎唔好令大家失望,因為我地呢班fans 都唔想大義滅親。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d18dc9f417bef33768f2a86ed92f729011b3473","tid":2090271,"uid":18584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:30:56.000Z","msg":"四川辣王踩踩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82579ce0a01b198029c0bbce0ba87745ce134bbb","tid":2090271,"uid":45572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:33:46.000Z","msg":"捐d屎就得"},{"pid":"2189ffc55fcab0494bc8ed97b16d3410e44662a7","tid":2090271,"uid":198810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:34:34.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n而家黃店連文宣都唔俾貼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2090235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2090235</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e746da619e9cc471cabaa317c76f8c4274401c70","tid":2090